* Configure Schema\nManaged Storage
** Optional but useful
***_ Separate physical storage per schema
***_ Compliance: financial data in specific accounts
** Requirements
***_ External location pre-configured
***_ CREATE MANAGED STORAGE privilege
** SQL syntax
***_ CREATE SCHEMA ... MANAGED LOCATION '...'
***_ abfss://container@account.dfs.core.windows.net/path
** Without schema storage
***_ Falls back to catalog's storage location
***_ Simplifies management when isolation not needed
@endmindmap
